    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-6 col-md-offset-0 col-lg-5">
      <h2>Developing an Online Database and Interface</h2>
      <p><strong>The Problem:</strong> Clients of techCorp requested a web-based corpus to share and organize documents produced by Technical Communication students.</p>
      <p><strong>The Solution:</strong> To create a simple, lightweight, and fast interface, I chose web technologies that could be used to prototype a RESTful application.</p><br>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-5 col-md-offset-2">
      <h5>My Role</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>Audience Analysis</li>
        <li>Database Design</li>
        <li>Web Development</li>
        <li>UI Design</li>
        <li>UX Testing</li>
      </ul><br>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-5">
